📄 [32m Final Result:[0m 
Yes, you can track your order through the IKEA website. On the IKEA US site, go to the "Track and manage your order" page (https://www.ikea.com/us/en/customer-service/track-manage-order/). There you can enter your order number and the email or phone number used for the purchase (or log in with your IKEA Family account) to view the status, details, and manage your order.

Steps to reach the page:
1. From the IKEA US homepage, scroll to the bottom and under the **Help** section click **My orders**, or use the direct link above.
2. On the "Track and manage your order" page, input the required information to track your order.

The page confirms that order tracking is available.


